{"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer\/textVariableAnchorOffset"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"provide an array of "},{"code":"textAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" locations, each paired with an offset value.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textJustify: auto"},{"type":"text","text":" to choose"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"justification based on anchor position."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression","text":"NSExpression"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used."},{"type":"text","text":" "